column7: You want to give this to me? Hmm, well, thanks. Here's something for you.
I thought maybe you'd try this again, so this time I was prepared. I brought something for you, as well.
Their scent is on the air...
I shall take care of this!
Glad you're still in one piece.
I want you to have this.
You should not have done that.
Is this intended as a joke?
I admit you know what you are doing.
You did not displease me... this time.
They are as good as dead!
You challenge me, Settrigh, and I shall hunt you down like a dog.
Anger me, and I shall decorate my sanctum with your pelt.
If you do not betray me, I shall have no cause to hunt you . Understand?
